# Bloom Coffee — Project Standards

## Stack

- Next.js App Router under `src/app/`
- Tailwind CSS v4 with theme tokens in `src/app/globals.css`
- Supabase for auth and PostgreSQL persistence

## Conventions

- Use TypeScript strict mode; shared types live in `src/lib/types.ts`
- Mutations use Server Actions in colocated `actions.ts` files
- Reusable UI lives in `src/components/ui/` — do not duplicate button/input styles inline
- Supabase clients: browser (`src/lib/supabase/client.ts`), server (`src/lib/supabase/server.ts`)
- Never commit secrets; use `.env.local` and document vars in `.env.example`
- Admin-only operations call `requireAdmin()` from the server module
- Revalidate customer routes (`/`, `/order`) after admin menu changes

## File naming

- Components: PascalCase (`DrinkCard.tsx`)
- Utilities: kebab-case or camelCase in `src/lib/`
- Routes: lowercase with hyphens for segments (`add-ons`)
